Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:22.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我们回到3万年前 狗狗诞生前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's go back across 30,000 years to a time before dogs,
