Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们对家的印象就是地球本身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their idea of home was Earth itself.
