Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大约在1万5千年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some 15,000 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个完美的生存策略\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an excellent survival strategy;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:01.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类的驯化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the domestication of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在人类捕猎时别威胁到他们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let the humans do the hunting, don't threaten them,
