Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随着这种不同物种间的合作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As this interspecies partnership continued over time,
