Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.62,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在冰河时代的间歇期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}during an intermission in the Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平和的气候带来了一场变革\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This break in the climate starts a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:37.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类不再流浪  而是定居下来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Instead of wandering, people are settling down.
