Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们依然在打猎和采集食物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People still hunt and gather,
