Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这保证了DNA的准确复制\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that the DNA is accurately copied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是没有什么是完美的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But nobody's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:10.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶尔 校对也会发生失误\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Occasionally, a proofreading error slips through,
