Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:17.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这头熊的卵子细胞中发生了突变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A mutation has occurred in the bear's egg cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:21.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此细微的随机事件也会带来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A random event as tiny as this one can have consequences
