Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:30.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突变改变了控制毛皮颜色的基因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That mutation altered the gene that controls fur color.
