Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它影响了这只熊的后代的深色毛皮的产生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the bear's offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大多数突变是无害的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most mutations are harmless.
