Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:42.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少数 纯属偶然 使得某个生物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But a few, purely by chance, can give an organism
