Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当两只熊长大到可以自己猎食时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When the cubs get old enough to venture out on their own,
