Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:08.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}棕熊和雪区别明显  很远就能被察觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The brown bear can be seen against the snow a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白熊子孙满堂 并把他独特的基因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The white bear prospers and passes on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}传递下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}its own particular set of genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的情况不断发生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This happens repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再接下去的几代里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Over succeeding generations,
