Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深色皮毛的基因消亡在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The gene for dark fur loses out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生存的竞争中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the competition for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:34.62,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突变是完全随机并且时刻发生的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mutations are entirely random and happen all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是环境会对奖励那些\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the environment rewards those
