Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:43.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大自然选择那些可以更好适应环境的生物\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It naturally selects the living things that are better suited to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:46.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种选择绝对不是随机的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that selection is the opposite of random.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两个种群的熊各自分开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The two populations of bears separated,
