Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是由猩猩进化而来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the thought that we share a common ancestor with the apes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:13.47,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我们的想法里 亲戚 最能让我们感到丢脸\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No one can embarrass you like a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的近亲  黑猩猩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our closest ones, the chimpanzees,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们频繁在公共场合做出不当的举止\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they frequently behave inappropriately in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类想和他们保持距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's an understandable human need
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是可以理解的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to distance ourselves from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}传统信仰的核心前提\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A central premise of traditional belief
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是造物者特制的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that we were created separately
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和其它动物有区别的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from all the other animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种观点也很容易被理解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's easy to see why this idea has taken hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它让我们觉得 与众不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It makes us feel... special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我们和这些树是亲戚呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what about our kinship with the trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又作何感想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How does that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是橡树DNA的一部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, here's a segment of the oak tree's DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把它看做条形码\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Think of it like a bar code.
