Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉这个树如何分解糖分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}tell the tree how to metabolize sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.28,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿它和我自己的DNA作比较\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now let's compare it with the same section of my own DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}DNA不会撒谎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The DNA doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这棵树就是我失散已久的表亲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This tree and me-- we're long-lost cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不单单是树\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's not just the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果回到很久以前 我们可以发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you go back far enough, you'll find that we share
