Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灰狼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}gray wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘑菇\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}mushroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鲨鱼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细菌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}bacterium...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻雀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多么幸福的一家人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:34.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}条形码的其它部分因人而异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Other parts of the bar code vary from species to species.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也使得猫头鹰和章鱼有所区别\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's what makes the difference between an owl and an octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非你有一个同卵双胞胎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Unless you have an identical twin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个世界上不会有人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's no one else in the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你有着相同的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&} with the exact same DNA as you.
