Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.52,0:35:51.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泰坦和地球有点像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Titan reminds me a little bit of home.
