Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.66,0:37:30.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事实上 这些风景和山脉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, the landscape and mountains
