Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.09,0:38:05.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种生物可能呼吸氢气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There might be creatures that inhale hydrogen
