Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.20,0:38:10.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呼出甲烷 而不是二氧化碳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And exhale methane instead of carbon dioxide.
