Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.17,0:38:16.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们怎样才能找到他们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How could we find out if such creatures
