Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.07,0:38:48.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算真有海怪在这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even if there is one of those down there,
