Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.25,0:39:06.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我们开点灯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's turn on some lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.49,0:39:13.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是表面下200米\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're now 200 meters beneath the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.20,0:39:19.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到什么了吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Did you see something?
