Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.42,0:39:40.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是最伟大的科学故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's the greatest story science has ever told.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.93,0:39:48.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关于我们世界上的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the story of life on our world.
