Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.61,0:40:31.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不怕承认我们不知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're not afraid to admit what we don't know.
