Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.99,0:40:53.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从现存的微生物得来的证据显示\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The evidence from living microbes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.86,0:40:55.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们最古老的祖先\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}suggest that their earliest ancestors
