Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.85,0:41:14.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从将近40亿年前的单细胞生物到你之间的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}directly from the one-celled organisms
