Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.99,0:41:26.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从不能分辨昼夜的生物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From creatures who had yet to discern day from night
